The paper discusses the use of machine learning techniques for detecting advanced malware, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also mentions the use of feature selection methods and multiple classifiers, which are common techniques in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The study also involves analyzing a dataset, which is a common task in data science (cs.DS) and software engineering (cs.SE).
